snippet.title: Superior: Vengeance
snippet.description:
Take on evil superheroes and steal their powers in this co-op, roguelite, third-person shooter.

Play on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1297490/Superior/

Learn more about Superior: Vengeance:
https://drifter.games/superiorvengeance
